v.name: Event_BetrayedByGuards
v.comment: On 01_AmbushBegins, when the player is ambushed, it'd be nice to have a dramatic sting as a lead in to normal combat music.

v.name: Event_EspinosaSpeaks
v.comment: When Audio_EspinosaSpeaks becomes active, Lord Espinosa addresses the planet and announces his takeover - be nice to have a brief musical interlude for this. This happens in the middle of a fight with ambushing tanks.

v.name: Event_AmbushOccurs
v.comment: Once 03_OccupyEvacZone becomes active until OccupyRegionObjective_EvacZone completes, we should probably enforce combat music even outside of interleaved mode - it's possible to kill the enemy very quickly and drop out of combat, but enemy reinfocements spawn every 2 turns and will do so until the objective is complete. It could be jarring without a manual enforcement of the combat music.

v.name: Event_VictoriaArrives
v.comment: When 05_VictoriaLance becomes active, we probably want custom music. This is the introduction of the big bad, and there won't be any combat. Just dialog and then a cinematic showing Mastiff "sacrificing" himself to save you (he lives, but it looks like he dies) and you have to flee.

v.name: 02_OnDialogEndLaunchArtillery
v.comment: This fires as soon as Alexander's call with you ends, after you arrive at Rotorua Township. This is where the artillery fires.

v.name: 05_ShiftTeamsActual
v.comment: This signals the final "boss" of mission 1b becoming active. He's a captain that Victoria's dispatched to assassinate you.
